lead_paragraph: Former U.S. Secretary of State Hillary Rodham Clinton says that Europe and the United States must nurture their ties because "there is no more important force for progress, prosperity and peace than the trans-Atlantic alliance."

headline.main: Hillary Clinton: US-Europe Must Nurture Ties
